column2: select source_id, ra, dec, parallax, parallax_error, pmra, pmra_error, pmdec, pmdec_error, parallax_pmra_corr, parallax_pmdec_corr, pmra_pmdec_corr, phot_g_mean_mag, bp_rp from gaiadr2.gaia_source where sqrt ((pmra-#) * (pmra-#) + (pmdec+#) * (pmdec+#) )< # and abs (b) > # and abs (parallax) < # into mydb.cps_gaia2_all
